0x870E8B40.name: GET_CALMING_QUAD_AT_COORDS
0x870E8B40.description: This native returns the index of a calming quad if the given point is inside its bounds.

examples.code:
local currentPedPosition = GetEntityCoords(PlayerPedId())
local calmingQuadIndex = GetCalmingQuadAtCoords(currentPedPosition.x, currentPedPosition.y)

0x870E8B40.resultsDescription: The calming quad index at the given position. Returns -1 if there isn't any there.
